Sentencas: The characteristics and performance of the anode-supported tubular cells with thin and dense Ba(Zr0.1Ce0.7-Y-0.2)O3-delta (BZCY) electrolyte was investigated.
Titulo: Fabrication of anode-supported tubular Ba(Zr0.1Ce0.7Y0.2)O3-δ cell for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The fine BZCY powder was prepared by a co-precipitation method.
Titulo: Fabrication of anode-supported tubular Ba(Zr0.1Ce0.7Y0.2)O3-δ cell for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The Ni-BZCY anode tube was fabricated by an extrusion process.
Titulo: Fabrication of anode-supported tubular Ba(Zr0.1Ce0.7Y0.2)O3-δ cell for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Ni-BZCY/BZCY nanocomposite slurry was coated on the anode tube as an anode fuctional layer (AFL) by using the dip-coating method.
Titulo: Fabrication of anode-supported tubular Ba(Zr0.1Ce0.7Y0.2)O3-δ cell for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The BZCY electrolyte and LSCF-BZCY cathode was coated by vacuum slurry coating and dip-coating method, respectively.
Titulo: Fabrication of anode-supported tubular Ba(Zr0.1Ce0.7Y0.2)O3-δ cell for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The anode tube had 0.381 mu m in pore size (porosity: 34%).
Titulo: Fabrication of anode-supported tubular Ba(Zr0.1Ce0.7Y0.2)O3-δ cell for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The impedance analysis of the tubular BZCY cells was conducted under open circuit condition.
Titulo: Fabrication of anode-supported tubular Ba(Zr0.1Ce0.7Y0.2)O3-δ cell for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The ohmic resistance and the polarization resistance of the BZCY electrolyte were about 0.78 Omega cm(2) and 0.035 Omega cm(2) at 700 degrees C, respectively.
Titulo: Fabrication of anode-supported tubular Ba(Zr0.1Ce0.7Y0.2)O3-δ cell for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The performance was measured under humidified H-2 (5% H2O) atmosphere at 600-700 C. The maximum power density of the tubular BZCY cell was about 0.5 Wcm(-2) at 700 degrees C. (C) 2013
Titulo: Fabrication of anode-supported tubular Ba(Zr0.1Ce0.7Y0.2)O3-δ cell for intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells
